
usage:
  1. cd to ./ping
  2. Edit './hosts' file to give have different ip addresses
  3. Copy ssh keys of remote machines/droplets by running this  commad
    ex: ssh-copy-id prod@169.14.7.126
        ssh-copy-id prod@169.14.7.127
    if dont want to save ssh keys try enabling in ansible.cfg
      #sudo_user      = root
      #ask_sudo_pass = True
      #ask_pass      = True

      
  4. folder and run this command:  'ansible-playbook -i hosts test.yml'
  5. you should success after ping resposes

  



